  "name": "Prophet's Luck",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You or a creature within range attempts a saving throw against an obvious threat.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You prophesize the result of the triggering saving throw as either a success (including a critical success) or a failure (including a critical failure). The target gains a +1 status bonus to the save if you predict success or a –1 status penalty if you predict failure. If you predict the result correctly, fortune favors you, and you gain a +1 status bonus to saving throws. If you predict incorrectly, fortune spurns the target, imparting a –1 status penalty to its saving throws.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (6th)</strong> The save bonus or penalty increases to +2 or –2.</p>\n<p><strong>Heightened (9th)</strong> The save bonus or penalty increases to +3 or –3.</p>"
